snippet.title: BANJO KAZOOIE - BOB OMB BATTLEFIELD (Playable Mod)
snippet.description:
#supermario64 #banjokazooie #Nintendo64
Created using Maya and Banjo's Backpack.
My own version of Bob-Omb Battlefield for Banjo Kazooie. I changed a lot of things and added a new areas. I hope you like it!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Markus_Kurko 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/Kurko_mods/
Support my Youtube channel : https://www.paypal.me/KurkoMods
